Other bits are the same.
========================= Low order bit ==========================
                    | REDUNDANT | COMPACT | COMPRESSED | DYNAMIC
dict_table_t::flags |     0     |    1    |     1      |    1
fil_space_t::flags  |     0     |    0    |     1      |    1
==================================================================
